AzureBlade remainded standing.

AzureBlade: I come straight from Earth, where both Predacons and
Maximals have taken refuge after the Tripredacus invasion of
Cybertron. The survivors have now formed a Council and have decreed
that all Maximals and Predacons must at least cooperate at resisting
the Tripredacus. My specific target is the Dark Optimus Prime. This is
why I come for your assistance. Prime is powerful and I need allies in
this endeavour.
